WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.066 --> 00:00:03.066
I can't just move in with you

2
00:00:03.066 --> 00:00:05.900
Your mom won't be happy if I move here

3
00:00:05.900 --> 00:00:09.633
That woman is not my mother

4
00:00:09.700 --> 00:00:11.833
So cold-blooded to his own daughter

5
00:00:11.866 --> 00:00:12.766
So be it, Shanshan

6
00:00:12.766 --> 00:00:16.100
I promise to see you often in the future, okay?

7
00:00:24.966 --> 00:00:25.966
Thank you

8
00:00:26.733 --> 00:00:29.900
Not hard, not like Mr. Bo

9
00:00:29.900 --> 00:00:33.000
She also coaxed Shanshan to pretend to lie to me.

10
00:00:34.400 --> 00:00:35.500
You know that?

11
00:00:35.733 --> 00:00:37.400
Of course I know.

12
00:00:37.466 --> 00:00:39.133
How do you teach kids to lie?

13
00:00:39.133 --> 00:00:40.466
Because he wants to see you

14
00:00:40.466 --> 00:00:41.600
I want to see you too.

15
00:00:42.066 --> 00:00:44.400
Shanshan wants to see me, I can understand

16
00:00:44.400 --> 00:00:46.066
What do you want to see me about?

17
00:00:46.400 --> 00:00:48.866
You say a man wants to meet a woman

